<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Twelve fragments of <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">revetment</rs>, some joining to form four groups. Average thickness: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.03</measure>.</p></div><div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of text</head><p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face, in two lines.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.12</measure> with broad flat trenches.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date cert="low" exact="none" notAfter="0200" notBefore="0101">Second century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
</div>
